data.description: Have your own Ponderosa! Beautiful acreage ready for your livestock operation. Improved pasture, Fenced and cross fenced pastures for rotating or separating livestock, covered working pens.2 Large hay barns, beautiful rolling hills with 3 ponds on the property.   Large shop that is set up as a feed store could be used for many application. Asphalt County road thru the property. Adorable farm house sits on the property open concept, 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, master bed room is downstairs with extra large closet and sitting area or room for a office.
